{"id": 752, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得生活中哪些地方需要熔断机制？", "description": "佛说，要冷静。（题图来自：Alex Andreyev）", "record_count": 3664, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021836085J7XnZ6aUobWFyYe.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-08T11:07:51Z", "options": [{"id": 44803, "content": "微信，每使用超过5分钟，熔断15分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 398290}, {"id": 40197, "content": "上课！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240814}, {"id": 40970, "content": "考试分数", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275654}, {"id": 40971, "content": "极品公婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407179}, {"id": 40460, "content": "哈哈不过估计就不会哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 332181}, {"id": 40212, "content": "玩手机，或者电脑游戏，玩一个小时熔断半小时，玩三个小时，熔断半天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406131}, {"id": 40214, "content": "Tfufheifhythiihhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415798}, {"id": 40218, "content": "熔断啥玩意", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247320}, {"id": 40476, "content": "股市经济熔断现象还不算硬伤，生活点点滴滴都会需要熔断机制！我们需要喘息的机会！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417534}, {"id": 43293, "content": "熔断什么意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436463}, {"id": 39970, "content": "支付宝。一阶段内消费家庭50％，冷却一周，消费70％，冷却一个月。——微博：香喷喷一锅肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 473, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 39971, "content": "手机自拍。自拍5张，冷却一小时，自拍10张基本一样的，关机。世界会很美好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 39972, "content": "乙方。方案修改5%以上，停工3小时，让甲方冷静一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 636, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 39973, "content": "吵架。怒火值超过正常情绪10%，自动失声；怒火值超过30%，自动睡眠。", "image": null, "praise_count": 424, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 42789, "content": "Work OT", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278073}, {"id": 40230, "content": "吃好吃的撑到爆，然后熔断10分钟，瞬间满血复活", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161514tAXKTH2IlSnoaJPq.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131997}, {"id": 39975, "content": "大姨夫来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260644}, {"id": 39976, "content": "体重，上了90，饭量冷却三个月，上了100，直接关机", "image": null, "praise_count": 265, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413381}, {"id": 39977, "content": "必然是考试时候答不出来50%的题的时候，允许上个厕所熔断会儿(●—●)", "image": null, "praise_count": 309, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274839}, {"id": 39978, "content": "上班，无聊指数50%以上，少量饮酒或运动，效果不明显，自动休息1天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296023}, {"id": 39980, "content": "请不要再伤害股民了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268211}, {"id": 39981, "content": "手机电量使用50%，熔断习惯性无脑乱刷微博、朋友圈功能。手机电量使用70%，熔断所有烧脑娱乐功能。直到插入充电器。", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2932}, {"id": 39982, "content": "房价", "image": null, "praise_count": 411, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287323}, {"id": 40494, "content": "加班。若连续三天加班，第四天必须提前一小时下班。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416632}, {"id": 39983, "content": "熔断式什么鬼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 388364}, {"id": 39984, "content": "考试时一道题超过5％的人不会写，熔断一下，让同学们讨论30分钟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 32364}, {"id": 39985, "content": "己方队友掉线，游戏暂停直到重新连接。敌方队友掉线。。。对不起比赛继续?", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380045}, {"id": 39987, "content": "老板布置工作超过正常量35%,熔断一下，理性委婉拒绝，等待谈判……", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413411}, {"id": 39988, "content": "当然是上网咯。五小时冷却半小时十小时冷却二十小时什么的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411492}, {"id": 39989, "content": "每日点赞超过5次，熔断一周", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219168}, {"id": 39990, "content": "妈妈啰嗦怎么还不结婚1分钟以上，熔断半小时，还能把话题捡起来，永久屏蔽关键词。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 39991, "content": "暗恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411017}, {"id": 39992, "content": "大概是双11吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209295}, {"id": 39993, "content": "为什么听装饮料要比塑料瓶装的好喝？", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 97301}, {"id": 40505, "content": "原来鼠绘那个是个骗局", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296525}, {"id": 41274, "content": "产品经理改需求1%，程序员停下来修养一个月先", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422276}, {"id": 39996, "content": "在公司内部我们也可以采用这种管理方法，比如: 当需求超过5%停止工作一小时，当用户反馈超过7％直接下班。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107787}, {"id": 42044, "content": "专家说的算", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289647}, {"id": 39997, "content": "能用于预防犯罪就好了，在它欲罪未罪之时触动熔断机制", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406637}, {"id": 39998, "content": "睡觉，睡五个小时要起来嘘嘘一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413491}, {"id": 40001, "content": "上厕所的时候超过三分钟，熔断，熔断……", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413522}, {"id": 40513, "content": "吃饭，玩手机的时候，饭菜总是做好了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417806}, {"id": 40002, "content": "中国的政府官员贪污超过10W直接下课，超过100W直接拉去枪毙！", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319545}, {"id": 40003, "content": "喝酒。喝五瓶，照照镜子，抽颗烟。喝十瓶，呵呵呵呵，呵呵呵呵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 387826}, {"id": 40259, "content": "熔断遗梦廊桥，\n熔断跨国购物，\n熔断非政府孔子和平奖和王一李丁气功神曲！\n熔断碎片社交自媒体残枝冷语，譬如我之声！？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416059}, {"id": 40004, "content": "考试季，然而我还在刷手机，so,NOW！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178901}, {"id": 40005, "content": "考试季，求放下手机！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178901}, {"id": 40006, "content": "ls说贪污的，还要10w才下课，难道不是只要贪污就下课吗，现在都是什么价值观啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 40012, "content": "工资下降百分之10，罢工一个月", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410403}, {"id": 40013, "content": "老板不给加薪，罢工了老板", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347374}]}